Subject: [PATCH 04/36] arm64: dts: qcom: sc7180-trogdor-pompom: rename
 5v-choke thermal zone

[ Upstream commit 9180b38d706c29ed212181a77999c35ae9ff6879 ]

Rename the 5v-choke thermal zone to satisfy the bindings.

